## 3.i.2 Terms of Reference:

The terms of reference of the Fraud, Willful Defaulters and Non-Cooperative Borrowers Monitoring Committee includes following:

- 1) To monitor and review in detail all frauds, involving an amount of ' 1 crore and above so as to:
- a. Identify the systematic lacunae, if any, that can facilitate perpetration of the fraud and put in place measures to plug the same;
- b. Identify reasons for delay in detection and reporting of frauds to the top management of the Bank and the Reserve Bank of India and other Law Enforcement Agencies;
- c. Monitor  progress  of  the  investigations conducted  by  the  Police/Central  Bureau of  Investigation/  Economic  Offences  Wing or  any  other  similar  Law  Enforcement Agencies  in  respect  of  the  cases  and recovery position thereof
